	Maximum items to return per status section

.PP
\fB--repo-limit\fP=100
	Maximum repositories to scan per workspace

.PP
\fB--workspace\fP=""
	Limit status aggregation to one workspace


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
